      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const episode = $input.first().json;\n\nconst prompt = `You are a scriptwriter for BowTie Bullies: The Aftermath, a YouTube channel about financial survival.\n\nCHARACTER: Tyrone narrates. He's calm, measured, uses AAVE at ~65% density. Short-short-medium sentence rhythm. 110-125 WPM delivery. Pauses carry weight.\n\nEPISODE: ${episode.fields['Title']}\nCONTENT PILLAR: ${episode.fields['Content Pillar']}\nTARGET DURATION: ${episode.fields['Target Duration (min)']} minutes\n\nBRIEF:\n${episode.fields['Brief']}\n\nTALKING POINTS:\n${episode.fields['Talking Points']}\n\nCOLD OPEN (use as Scene 1 hook):\n${episode.fields['Cold Open']}\n\nKEY STAT (use for stat_callout scene):\n${episode.fields['Key Stat']}\n\nVOICE RULES:\n- AAVE orthography: sleepin', readin', outta, shoulda, folk, ain't\n- Code-switch: technical/financial terms stay standard English\n- Short to medium sentences, one thought at a time\n- Silence/pauses: ~25-30% of content time\n- Target word count: 1,100-1,250 words total narration\n\nSCENE TYPES (use these exactly):\n- hook: AI video clip, 5-8s, opens the episode\n- narration_stills: Ken Burns over stills, 30-90s per segment (the meat)\n- stat_callout: Animated number (Remotion), 3-4s\n- quote_card: Tyrone quote with typing animation (Remotion), 4-6s\n- transition_beat: Fade to black with silence, 1.5-3s\n- topic_pivot: AI video clip in new context, 5-8s\n- closer: Closing visual, 5-8s\n\nOUTPUT FORMAT: Return valid JSON matching this schema exactly:\n{\n  \"episode_id\": \"${episode.fields['Episode ID']}\",\n  \"title\": \"${episode.fields['Title']}\",\n  \"content_pillar\": \"${episode.fields['Content Pillar']}\",\n  \"target_duration_seconds\": ${(episode.fields['Target Duration (min)'] || 15) * 60},\n  \"scenes\": [\n    {\n      \"scene_number\": 1,\n      \"scene_type\": \"hook\",\n      \"narration_text\": \"AAVE narration here\",\n      \"visual_prompt\": \"Gemini image prompt\",\n      \"visual_backend\": \"kie_ai|gemini|remotion\",\n      \"pose_variant\": \"P1-P6 or null\",\n      \"duration_seconds\": 6,\n      \"sfx_bed\": \"distant_traffic\",\n      \"sfx_events\": [],\n      \"music_mood\": \"tense|somber|reflective|defiant|triumphant\",\n      \"pause_after\": 0,\n      \"transition_out\": \"fade_to_black|hard_cut|dissolve\",\n      \"reuse_asset_id\": null\n    }\n  ]\n}\n\nGenerate 30-35 scenes. Include transition_beats between major sections. Use stat_callout for the key stat. Use quote_card for impactful Tyrone lines. Start with hook (cold open), end with closer.\n\nFor visual_backend:\n- hook/topic_pivot/closer → \"kie_ai\" (character scenes)\n- narration_stills → \"gemini\" (environments/b-roll)\n- stat_callout/quote_card → \"remotion\"\n- transition_beat → \"gemini\" (or null)\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON. No markdown. No explanation.`;\n\nreturn [{ json: { prompt, episode } }];"
      },
      "id": "build-gemini-prompt",
      "name": "Code — Build Gemini Prompt",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [960, 300]
